        Return the radical of ``self``, the product of the irreducible
        factors of the polynomial. This is also referred to as the
        square-free part of the polynomial.

            >>> R = fmpz_mod_poly_ctx(163)
            >>> x = R.gen()
            >>> f = (x + 1)**3 * (x + 2)
            >>> f.radical()
